                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            etype 0x8847
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 633 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8848/MPLS multicast/Broadcast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                            etype 0x8848
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 666 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8848/MPLS multicast/Multicast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac 01:00:5e:00:00:00 ff:ff:ff:80:00:00
                            etype 0x8848
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 699 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8848/MPLS multicast/Others"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            etype 0x8848
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 733 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8863/PPPoE Discovery/PADI/Broadcast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                            etype 0x8863
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 766 create
                        action accept

                cbs 50

            exit

            exit

                    queue 1
                exit
            exit

                multicast-queue 12
                queue 2
                egress-hsmda
                    queue 6
                exit
            exit

                multicast-queue 13
                queue 3
                egress-hsmda
                    queue 5
                exit
            exit
        exit

            high-slope
                start-avg 80
                max-avg 95
                max-prob 10
                no shutdown
            exit
            low-slope
                start-avg 30
                max-avg 95
                max-prob 20
                no shutdown
            exit
        exit
    exit

        network 100 create
            description "NETWORK QoS POLICY Ingress classification,Egress remarking "
            ingress
                default-action fc be profile in
                dscp be fc be profile out
                dscp cs1 fc ef profile in
                dscp cs2 fc ef profile in
                dscp cs3 fc ef profile in
                dscp cs4 fc h2 profile in
                dscp cs5 fc ef profile in
                dscp nc1 fc h2 profile in
                dscp nc2 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 0 fc be profile out
                lsp-exp 1 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 2 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 3 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 4 fc h2 profile in
                lsp-exp 5 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 6 fc h2 profile in
                lsp-exp 7 fc ef profile in
            exit
            egress
                remarking
                fc ef
                    dscp-in-profile cs5
                    dscp-out-profile cs5
                exit
                fc h2
                    dscp-in-profile cs4
                    dscp-out-profile cs4
                exit
            exit
        exit
    exit
